jsx.http.rpc.remote
Class Objective

java.lang.Object
  jsx.http.rpc.remote.Objective
Direct Known Subclasses:
CObject
public abstract class Objective
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract base class for client-side non-disposable reflected objects that are finalized automatically once out of reference.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org

Method Detail

finalize

protected void finalize()

Finalizes this object when all the references to it are out of scope.

This method decreases the reference count of the remote object that reflects this one by calling Reflector.decrease(ArrayLike, jsx.Returnable) without a Returnable.

Overrides:
finalize in class java.lang.Object
